Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:09.00,CRZero,all,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:12.39,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Gallia's capital, Lutis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.11,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Tabitha is from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.55,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure we can \Nask you to repair the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.46,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've used up my \Nluck as a researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.34,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I get to see another \Nbarbarian country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.01,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew this was going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:27.97,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I would have insisted on \Nfollowing Lord Bidalsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:29.85,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sigh like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:32.02,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as our \Nhoneymoon and enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:34.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did that Saito go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:39.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sait—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa said you'd have \Ntrouble without this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:44.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.69,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:55.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the "Tiffa, Tiffa" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:59.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was your master first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:03.24,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're Tiffa's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:04.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:06.93,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you were \Nable to win with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito prefers them small!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:13.25,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:16.60,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you happily touching her breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:19.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:20.39,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:25.16,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.66,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,I am so relieved you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.34,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Start preparing the coronation \Nceremony right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So she decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.98,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}Tabitha's Coronation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.52,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,We need more stuffing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.78,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to lay eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.13,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.74,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.77,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,So you made the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.72,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha is going to be a queen soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.65,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Miss Tabitha will be quite pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.98,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,at the coronation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.12,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:07.04,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,"This is the last chance to lay eggs!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.84,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,That's what that rhyme dragon will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.66,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,and try to get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.69,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha is too busy preparing for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.30,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:20.21,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a hidden room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.41,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Like here, or here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.41,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.49,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.93,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,She might be more of a \Ndanger than Miss Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.03,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Miss Westwood is \Nalso Saito's master now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The second! I was his master first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.69,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,The order doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.12,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is what Saito thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course he's going to choose me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is that stupid dog doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.67,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, a little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.17,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.30,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Lower? Okay, now I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Do tell, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.22,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to get the bug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A bug? Please, try to think \Nof a more plausible lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.91,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really. Like a bug would
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.68,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,oh so conveniently get into her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that's solved, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.88,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:45.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You should depend on me more. \NI'm your familiar after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.61,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.97,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Then please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're going to the \Nguest house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys were on my mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.75,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that they \Nmight feel a bit lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.79,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be best to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.10,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,it's clear who the real master is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.63,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Explore the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.23,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Don't you want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.83,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,the other buildings now that we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.83,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:31.49,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing more jail-like buildings \Nwould just be depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.12,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.81,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.88,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.62,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm captain of the Order \Nof the Undine Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:44.13,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche de Gramont.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.99,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Malicorne de Grandple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.02,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.34,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to show \Nme around the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:55.74,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but we can't \Nlet you leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.06,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl with the blue hair \Nsaid I was free to do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.98,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what Tabitha said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.30,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't have you cause \Nany commotion right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.62,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.91,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody found out that \Nthey're hiding elves here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.45,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,you can forget about the coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.51,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.39,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.45,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here quietly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.55,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,With you as our guards, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:23.18,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just a tiny bit. \NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.20,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.97,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Please go back. I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.50,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.43,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you touch Lukshana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.21,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought I was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.02,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.58,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,You elves are truly uncivilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.92,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Uncivilized?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.09,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ultimate insult, \Ncoming from a barbarian!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need anythi—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.57,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,This barbarian manhandled Lukshana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.51,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.78,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:13.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, who cares? Just put that \Naway and let's get along, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.78,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,You say get along, but you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.75,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,No way, not with someone who \Nlooks down on others like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,He's just putting up a tough front
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,because he's in a totally foreign place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You can relate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.22,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I think they'd understand \Nif they'd just talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wh-what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm choosing what to wear to the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha provided me with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:47.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there is a dance after \Nthe coronation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:57.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's more for girls \Nwith a bigger chest, like Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is better for you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try it on, so help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Help me with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you won't \Nlisten to your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you my familiar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to tie the ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can touch them if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.06,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I said just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.09,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only master for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of c—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.61,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:24.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.59,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having trouble putting this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:31.84,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to depend on you \Nfor things like this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:37.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! These things \Nshould be done by girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It seems to be a bit tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:50.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.47,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow, Tabitha will be a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.48,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, she'll be of the \Nsame standing as Lady Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.04,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, I heard she just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.48,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Lukshana is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.77,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.95,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to take a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.33,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,but since she was taking \Nso long, I went in to check
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.67,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,and she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:21.63,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.29,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.40,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Go find her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.37,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This has been irking me since before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.32,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,but what's with your tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.86,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you ask people for favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.34,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Can it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.56,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what \Nyou were guarding us for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:37.85,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,We're not standing guard for you, \Nwe're doing it for Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.18,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.99,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,You two, don't start this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.65,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.63,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.63,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness? You mean from Romalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.62,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. If this gets out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.86,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find Lukshana before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What? Lukshana is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.58,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:07.17,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she got captured by \Nbarbarians and is being abused...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She's got her wits together, \Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:16.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help look for her, \Nbut the queen summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.09,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.56,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.73,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find her, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.73,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It's primitive, but very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:51.82,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to congratulate you on \Nyour coronation, Queen Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.45,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:58.30,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Saito and Miss Westwood, \NI'm relieved you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:04.56,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, we should have \Ncome to rescue you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.20,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised you were able to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.34,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,rescue those two from \Nthose unknown lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to, I was casting a spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.32,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You can use a World Door...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.25,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,World Door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:30.99,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Void spell that can \Nconnect two distant places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.04,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, so you learned a new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:38.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I actually almost ran out of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but when I grabbed Saito's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,the window got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.55,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Got bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.03,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the power \Nof the spell got stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:53.07,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,But Gandalfr shouldn't \Nhave that kind of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.61,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I think this has something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:02.99,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:08.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently I've become \NTiffa's familiar as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.07,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.33,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,One body can house multiple \Nfamiliar powers, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.93,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:23.49,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that Lífþrasir is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Líf... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:31.90,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Lífþrasir is someone who has the \Nability to amplify the Void powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:35.85,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,That's what caused the surge \Nof power in Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:41.71,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph's familiar was the \NMind of God, Mioznitnirn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.92,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's the Left \NHand of God, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.33,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,The Right Hand of God, Windalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.77,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And the Heart of God, Lífþrasir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.57,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Four familiars to fight alongside \Nthe four Void Mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.93,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that the four \Nand four exist to join
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.32,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,their powers in order to \Nsave Halkeginia from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.50,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,As we have not found Joseph's successor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.77,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,the four and four are \Ncurrently incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.20,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Halkeginia were to face a crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.89,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we have Lífþrasir,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.13,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,we can amplify our powers many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.60,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Lífþrasir is wonderful news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I have that kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess it's basically a booster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So using this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,your Explosion would get \Nmuch stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.56,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe this means that me binding
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.42,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the contract with Saito had its use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:57.15,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, perhaps there was a \Npoint to my feelings, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.97,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are. \NWe were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.48,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,We were thinking of \Ngoing to Tabitha's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.02,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's the last night, \Nwe wanted to spend it with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:11.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good. I'm in. \NTiffa, you'll come too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.52,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.22,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. No boys allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.89,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:31.23,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Tabitha will be surprised \Nwhen all of us suddenly show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.67,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,She's got blond hair like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.64,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,and breasts like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:41.57,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche, I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:46.60,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, M-Montmorency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.50,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I let you out of my sight for \None second and this happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.23,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think, Montmorency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.86,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually looking \Nfor someone. Right now—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.99,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.50,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You really never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.74,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Montmorency!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.49,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:13.81,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.68,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.60,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that elves and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.22,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,barbarians are the same \Nwhen it comes to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.73,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,You have it quite rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.36,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.23,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,When he has someone like me?! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.07,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Lukshana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.59,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't in the guest house?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.54,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I simply had to see the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.78,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it'd \Nlead to such a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.83,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,So, what Guiche said back there... Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.94,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,was he looking for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:54.95,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.42,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.15,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for not being clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:03.93,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,That's often why Ari and I fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.10,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we'll get along quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.80,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.60,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.99,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to look \Nfor Lukshana any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.04,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,She always does what she wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.78,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,but if I dare to voice my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.93,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,she immediately threatens \Nto not marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:31.96,CRZero,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she knows that \NI can't say anything then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.19,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.16,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,If I even talk to another girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.13,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,she screams that I'm cheating on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:42.40,CRZero,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Women are so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:48.02,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like those two are \Nbest buddies all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just glad they get along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder where Lukshana is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.24,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Malicorne!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lukshana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:04.78,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell Ari that Lukshana \Nwill stay over here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.68,CRZero,Lukshana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.04,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Lukshana and Montmorency, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.77,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. They'll understand \Nif they just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.43,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I, Charlotte Helene Orléans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:49.97,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,hereby proclaim that I \Nwill be Queen of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.30,CRZero,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,My Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.34,CRZero,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,A new queen has been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha is queen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that thing we \Ndiscussed the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:09.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,About me being your only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean that "master" and \Nall that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The only one I love is you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up or you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:32.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But... Wait, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't finished putting on my dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Man, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:45.59,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, why didn't \Nyou tell Saito about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.14,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,About Lífþrasir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:52.29,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Indeed, it amplifies \Nthe power of the Void,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.45,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,but the energy of his soul can never be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.68,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,replenished once it's used.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.17,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,If he keeps using it, Saito will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.38,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of Lífþrasir is
