Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.86,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,When he runs out of energy, he will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.45,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,But telling him this would only
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:13.02,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,strike unnecessary fear into his heart.
