Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:29.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Lífþrasir \Nthat Saito has gained...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected that the time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,it's truly needed would come so soon.
